Develop media statements and speeches for the MMC; 
Compile responses to media enquiries; 
Build relations with the media and promote the portfolio of the MMC and the department; 
Participate in forums and in the collective planning of the communication and media issues of the Municipality; 
Liaise with key internal and external stakeholders in the department to ensure coordination and alignment of communication priorities and programmes. 

Leading Competencies: 
Business acumen; 
Project management; 
Work independently; 
People management; 
Event management. 

